snippet.title: "Christmas with Weezer" IOS game - BONUS VIDEO
snippet.description:
This video would be viewable after beating all the levels in the IOS game "Christmas wirh Weezer". It features a clip of Rivers Cuomo directly addressing the player, along with footage of an interview being conducted with the band, a short clip of the band performing Only In Dreams live (with Pat on vocals), and a video of Pat playing a harp.

Video ripped directly from the game's files.

For more info on "Christmas with Weezer":
https://www.weezerpedia.com/wiki/Christmas_with_Weezer
Download the app's file:
https://archive.org/details/christmas-with-weezer-app
